WEBVTT

01:02.462 --> 01:05.495
Last night,
I dreamt of a steady,

01:05.498 --> 01:08.401
cool rain falling out
of the African sky,

01:09.436 --> 01:11.701
soaking me to my bones.

01:14.740 --> 01:18.208
I watched as my filth
pooled at my feet,

01:18.210 --> 01:21.180
the raindrops washing
away my stories.

01:22.748 --> 01:23.816
That I was free.

01:29.188 --> 01:34.193
But then I awoke, choking on
the dust of this dry place.

01:36.328 --> 01:38.529
And I wondered if
hope does exist

01:38.531 --> 01:40.198
for people who are desperate

01:40.200 --> 01:42.201
and have nothing
else to cling to.

01:44.837 --> 01:46.105
I have to know.

01:47.807 --> 01:49.542
Because if hope is stupid,

01:52.879 --> 01:54.514
why would anything matter?

02:02.287 --> 02:04.689
Balls, it is so
effin' hot out here.

02:04.691 --> 02:05.823
